description:
A staple condiment in every household, Fountain Tomato Sauce pairs well with almost any meal. Made with no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives, enjoy it with eggs for breakfast, a wrap for lunch and barbecued meat for dinner.

A staple condiment in every household, Fountain Tomato Sauce pairs well with almost any meal. Made with no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives, enjoy it with eggs for breakfast, a wrap for lunch and barbecued meat for dinner. A necessity for all barbecues, Fountain Tomato Sauce will meet all your saucing needs. Gluten free with no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives, dip almost anything into this tomato sauce including hot chips, wedges and onion rings.

Tomato sauce

Perfect for hot chips, burgers and sausage sizzles

No artificial colours or flavours

No preservatives

Gluten free
